BOX-sizing : The CSS box-sizing property allows us to include the padding and border in an element's total width and height.

*{                  /*this is done for universality of the webpage in different browsers*/
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;      /*The CSS box-sizing property allows us to include the padding and border in an element's total width and height.*/
}

this is the basic reset using css!!!!!



